title: Hari impungenge ko umubyeyi ubana naVirusi itera SIDA ashobora kwanduza umwana we binyuze mu mashereka.
content:
Hari impungenge ko umubyeyi ubana naVirusi itera SIDA ashobora kwanduza umwana we binyuze mu mashereka. Niyo mpamvu umubyeyi wese ubana na Virusi itera SIDA agomba kwitwararika mu gukurikiza inama za muganga no kunywa imiti 
neza kugira ngo atanduza umwana we.
